{"tid":307841,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我扮左34年精神病患者","createTime":"2017-07-03T16:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T16:50:44.000Z","uid":123335,"like":219,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a5abcd0b7a8b72fb8a8a870c2e685549c0d4dc","tid":307841,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:06:13.000Z","msg":"我10歲果陣，讀緊小學五年級<br />\n我最撚憎就係讀書<br />\n最鍾意就係打機 睇電視<br />\n<br />\n由於成日唔溫書<br />\n掛住睇有線兒童台晚晚7點播既飛天小女警<br />\n我爛grade <br />\n讀得好差<br />\n<br />\n我呀媽見我成日唔讀書走去玩<br />\n就屈鳩我有過度活潑症（ADHD) <br />\n帶我去睇醫生<br />\n迫鳩我食果d Ritalin ，一種中樞神經系統興奮劑"},{"pid":"4519a4300423a13dd2f0ed52ac1bfaf53b46d469","tid":307841,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:08:35.000Z","msg":"繼續"},{"pid":"69ada6a1f9b3141fe028d38f8708f4b75f2d5aa1","tid":307841,"uid":3814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:09:13.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d2c4c91f579ce627e8734789cdb4db0cf0706e","tid":307841,"uid":89337,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:11:01.000Z","msg":"見到你user name叫自己做博士 你唔似扮喎 Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa74c11b23ca330de80ccd19ee071557abc43e9e","tid":307841,"uid":54728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:13:26.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"1cbbb3690c33e92a18d8641f28e9ddc492486836","tid":307841,"uid":123335,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:13:34.000Z","msg":"點解老母要屈鳩我睇精神科去食藥？<br />\n因為我呀媽好要面子 ，佢係一位律師，短髮女強人，唔衰得俾街外人睇<br />\n我小5 小6 成績表要呈分<br />\n所以佢用極端手段<br />\n屈鳩我係ADHD 迫我食藥去讀書考試，提升分數，入讀Band 1 英中<br />\n<br />\n我小學讀書已經使用禁藥<br />\n呢件事當然冇街外人知<br />\n學校老師見就的成績突飛猛進固然驚訝<br />\n同學都嚇左一跳<br />\n我食藥後短短2個月<br />\n已經成為班中既頭三甲學生 <br />\n<br />\n但<br />\n世上冇咁便宜既事<br />\n隻藥係有副作用"},{"pid":"bf6ae9da4e565b49e7f8339dc277d6f4b38ab131","tid":307841,"uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:21:32.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"bc891979dd5f2b02b828b63eb5fd67c9774ddf07","tid":307841,"uid":55513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:22:54.000Z","msg":"好似故仔<br />\n<br />\nbtw支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3809b7cca75688b693238f07ce6c73aeeb66b504","tid":307841,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:24:46.000Z","msg":"快點"},{"pid":"a9c2e15d05ebe476fc93c3c352baef5d01a178ee","tid":307841,"uid":63392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:24:51.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186a66e742bfa024883a0c6f89cdb7fc61985101","tid":307841,"uid":101253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:29:44.000Z","msg":"咁撚似劉馬車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開頭"},{"pid":"02e041fb45bd369629fd0bd5d117041269623be3","tid":307841,"uid":59612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:31:29.000Z","msg":"留名睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2bb0454f29781b2b783211909f88ee488a21c66","tid":307841,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16ef0802fe0ff68be33963571189cbfc096fff4","tid":307841,"uid":106922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2b94de5309ecefcc927a46ae6b5c9cd0b653f9eb","tid":307841,"uid":43557,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:37:32.000Z","msg":"食禁藥笑到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c3a6e091695db2c5a894bfd49220e0ce30c86f","tid":307841,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:48:56.000Z","msg":"初初食隻藥 <br />\n一食完會冇晒七情六慾，<br />\n平時追住晚晚睇既叔比狗，東京Mew Mew，飛天小女警<br />\n而家已經興趣大減 <br />\n見到平時好愛食熱辣辣 香噴噴既牛油粟米，<br />\n見到都冇feel ，冇晒食慾<br />\n<br />\n藥效啟動後<br />\n眼下既世界只淨下理性<br />\n<br />\n表情麻木既我  <br />\n平時見到同學唔會識笑 <br />\n我外表上成碌木咁<br />\n木獨既氣場，亦令到我成為被欺凌既對象<br />\n有一次早會排隊果陣，我俾一個同校巴既小3同學用飛腳一野踢落我個雞心<br />\n痛到出唔到聲真係 <br />\n呢一腳，完全冇先兆，完全唔知點解踢我<br />\n或者，真係樣既問題，You face you fate ... <br />\n<br />\n儘管我食完藥後成個碌柒咁<br />\n但實際上， I see everything <br />\n我大腦非常清晰當下發生既每一個微小既細節  <br />\n我知道，我唔識笑，唔識一齊同人玩，太理性既刻板型象係主因<br />\n我俾佢踢完一腳後，我冇告發佢，亦冇打算報復，<br />\n反而，我放學後去OK買左包魚仔餅，紫菜味<br />\n隔日早上塔校巴果陣，用木獨既口吻請佢食<br />\n見佢佢笑笑口好開心咁<br />\n我心想: Problem solved <br />\n<br />\n食完藥好似變左神童咁變成班中頭幾名，順利入讀第一志願<br />\n係一間港島中西區既Band 1英中名校<br />\n聽落好似好成功？ 邁向人生勝利組？<br />\n<br />\n其實背後<br />\n我唔止一次因為木獨既形象而俾人恰，被欺凌<br />\n呢d 童年陰影真係有苦自己知，直到依家人到中年都揮之不去<br />\n另外，隻藥會伴隨頭痛，胃痛，失眠，脫髮，影響發育...等既副作用<br />\n話說...我成年後身高得161cm <br />\n學生時代想識女仔, 一直都係收卡下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286320d4b1def84666eed21676ce3cece1663df8","tid":307841,"uid":103229,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:51:52.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b3a8ce078bf676e6433120569260598c9af4cc","tid":307841,"uid":47055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"df013b578b1cb9e676bda189ebc791640c82e9d9","tid":307841,"uid":65186,"like":181,"dislike":1,"score":180,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>初初食隻藥 <br />\n一食完會冇晒七情六慾，<br />\n平時追住晚晚睇既叔比狗，東京Mew Mew，飛天小女警<br />\n而家已經興趣大減 <br />\n見到平時好愛食熱辣辣 香噴噴既牛油粟米，<br />\n見到都冇feel ，冇晒食慾<br />\n<br />\n藥效啟動後<br />\n眼下既世